Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.70,0:01:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.98,0:01:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,600)}{\fs40}名为α的野兽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.08,0:01:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…莫非是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.22,0:01:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.25,0:02:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回家 莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.91,0:02:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这样擅自行动可不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.39,0:02:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就知道你会来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.72,0:02:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.62,0:02:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉拉·琉特鲁公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.88,0:02:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是长大了不少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.57,0:02:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露西尔·艾利斯君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.13,0:02:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他现在还不到可以看「门」的阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.84,0:02:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是由你来决定的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.47,0:02:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您果然是个阻碍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.90,0:02:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你猜这个是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.02,0:03:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇者遗物吗 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.97,0:03:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种东西可是杀不了我的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.36,0:03:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.66,0:03:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.71,0:03:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粉碎吧 神兽灭绝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.79,0:03:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次见面之前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.39,0:03:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要找到可以杀死你的咒语才行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.56,0:03:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露西尔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.40,0:03:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.95,0:03:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉特鲁公爵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.51,0:03:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.36,0:03:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不像你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.79,0:03:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么没杀了他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.60,0:04:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那口气 倒是越来越像样了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.26,0:04:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉拉·琉特鲁公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.84,0:04:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将那侵蚀罗兰德的该死亡灵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.92,0:04:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.24,0:04:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.93,0:04:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.30,0:04:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我不知不觉中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.27,0:04:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界似乎起了巨大的变化
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.50,0:04:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是我理想中的王者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.98,0:04:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切遵照您的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.45,0:04:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.31,0:04:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了拯救…这腐朽的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.49,0:04:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天叫你来不为别的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.86,0:04:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想知道你的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.39,0:04:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我不满意你的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.43,0:05:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.06,0:05:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.25,0:05:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就听听吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.75,0:05:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问吧 露西尔·艾利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.36,0:05:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道你会这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.40,0:05:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.45,0:05:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会再驻足不前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.66,0:05:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻挡在眼前的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.84,0:05:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是谁都杀无赦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.82,0:05:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此我什么都能接受
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.97,0:05:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.53,0:05:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直 一直在等待
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.66,0:05:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 成为吾主
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.49,0:06:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抛弃一切
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.04,0:06:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将一切献作祭品
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.39,0:06:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为吾剑之主吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.46,0:06:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你将是吞噬 开拓这世界的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.77,0:06:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.08,0:06:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 拯救世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.05,0:06:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.25,0:06:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会让你为所欲为
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.52,0:06:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会让你为所欲为
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.42,0:06:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即将消失的假货还能有合作为
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.82,0:06:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡说八道 你才是假货
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.56,0:06:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.14,0:06:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你会输
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.73,0:06:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不认为那笨蛋轻易就会死…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.53,0:06:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 站住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.74,0:07:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟有美丽的小姐跟我搭话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.03,0:07:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真幸运
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.79,0:07:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子 到底对莱纳做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.05,0:07:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.99,0:07:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢莱纳吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.50,0:07:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.89,0:07:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.58,0:07:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.26,0:07:27.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.03,0:07:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺有一套嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.24,0:07:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还真想多看看你的真本领
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.34,0:07:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道你有什么目的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.65,0:07:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但若敢小看我 小心没命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.75,0:07:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁会没命？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.80,0:07:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.28,0:07:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重量大概三倍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.34,0:07:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别想了 你没有胜算的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.48,0:08:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 你问我对莱纳做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.08,0:08:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我杀了他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.61,0:08:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用小刀插进他的心脏杀了他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.14,0:08:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他血流如注 表情甚是可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.21,0:08:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.28,0:08:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我没说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.49,0:08:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳死了 你明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.61,0:08:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀 惹哭你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.68,0:08:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.30,0:08:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.72,0:08:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要…杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.99,0:08:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合格
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.96,0:08:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉这么欺负你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.20,0:08:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你如此重视莱纳…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.74,0:08:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.47,0:09:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.24,0:09:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起源（α）即破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.66,0:09:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾不行创造 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.75,0:09:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行惠泽 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.91,0:09:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行拯救
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.12,0:09:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅行消除 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.62,0:09:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回归纯白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.73,0:09:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一天吾等了好久

Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.48,0:10:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟以为这种仿冒品就能封住吾等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.64,0:10:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但一切都结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.16,0:10:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吞噬了你 便能解除这封印吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.30,0:10:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾将前往「α」 一切遵照契约
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.41,0:10:13.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失吧 解开所有公式者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.34,0:10:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人体实验？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.94,0:10:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.18,0:10:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有报告说其发狂后从实验设施逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.25,0:10:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个破忌者　因为被施过禁忌之术
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.03,0:10:34.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,获得了超越常人的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.09,0:10:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀 杀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.47,0:10:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 阿斯塔尔陛下即位以来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.61,0:10:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人体实验应该被禁止了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.60,0:10:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是罗兰德帝国破忌者追击部队队长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.22,0:10:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜尔可·卡拉德中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.97,0:10:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你习得了罗兰德魔法…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.51,0:10:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.88,0:11:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托 听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.97,0:11:12.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上头有令 那个破忌者杀无赦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.76,0:11:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下知道这件事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.61,0:11:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 因为人体实验是陛下的指令
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.96,0:11:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下他…正常吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.56,0:11:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 无比正常
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.35,0:11:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是因为有必要才重新开始这种实验
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.18,0:11:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都知道这件事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.36,0:11:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是…卢克你们一直瞒着我的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.53,0:12:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗兰德的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.26,0:12:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以…解脱了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.59,0:12:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了…就能解脱了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.49,0:12:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.95,0:12:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以活着长大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.45,0:12:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会和我结婚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.39,0:12:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果幸存下来 能和我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.54,0:12:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间到 过来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.21,0:12:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.72,0:12:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算约定…也没有意义啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.52,0:12:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我是要死的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.36,0:12:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.92,0:12:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊 太爱哭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.87,0:12:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要说什么要死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.09,0:12:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能行的啦 这么顽强
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.79,0:12:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也没打算死呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.09,0:12:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.46,0:13:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 你也别死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.97,0:13:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.95,0:13:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.56,0:13:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没能救你 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.85,0:13:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能这样做 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.29,0:13:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使接下来即将发生一切
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.53,0:13:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都在陛下的剧本之中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.09,0:13:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.87,0:13:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所生存的国度 我一定会守护到底
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.55,0:13:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 阿特法尔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.97,0:13:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种程度的诅咒就想压制我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.22,0:14:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.62,0:14:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.05,0:14:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…谁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.95,0:14:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你长得…这么大了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.40,0:14:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉拉 是你给了我时间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.83,0:14:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在等你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.41,0:14:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只为了见你 一直在等待
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.82,0:14:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了…见我？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.34,0:14:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱你 莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.01,0:14:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.70,0:14:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在「编造所有公式者」出现之前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.39,0:14:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快往深处去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.66,0:14:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后去触碰「门」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.30,0:15:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,门？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.12,0:15:05.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了守护你珍重的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.33,0:15:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,区区一个祭品 大胆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.87,0:15:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大胆大胆大胆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.58,0:15:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想再多碰碰你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.71,0:15:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再多说几声我爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.96,0:15:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想一直陪在你身边 看着你成长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.16,0:15:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶…可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.73,0:15:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底要我做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.32,0:15:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.79,0:15:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也要在此成为吾之祭品
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.70,0:16:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救…救…我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.75,0:16:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要…将你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.55,0:16:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想…吃了你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.45,0:16:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.82,0:16:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.53,0:16:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得是突然被奇怪的家伙捅了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.01,0:16:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.80,0:16:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…早
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.60,0:16:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.40,0:17:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混账莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.72,0:17:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是逃避的你 无法拯救莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.35,0:17:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃避的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.09,0:17:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以拯救世界为借口
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.63,0:17:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你出卖了莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.59,0:17:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.57,0:17:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要闭嘴的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.08,0:17:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.58,0:17:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳不会放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.73,0:17:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别满口空想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.59,0:17:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃避选择 逃避恐惧 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.03,0:17:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃避痛苦的你救不了莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.99,0:17:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我选择了 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.62,0:17:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选择向前进
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.40,0:17:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不让你得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.84,0:17:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就从黑暗中拯救莱纳看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.95,0:17:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你做不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.60,0:17:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你做得到 我早就做了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.32,0:17:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此 我还是要救莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.92,0:17:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.09,0:17:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.03,0:17:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会杀了莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.15,0:17:58.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在他陷入黑暗之前救他出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.52,0:18:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只要睡着就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.98,0:18:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会终结一切
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.23,0:18:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 到底谁赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.45,0:18:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定了吧 要怎么处置莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.72,0:18:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 你也不记得发生了什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.41,0:18:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好像有人告诉了我什么很重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.32,0:19:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.54,0:19:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是啥

Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.74,0:20:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解开所有公式者…是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.65,0:20:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 你竟然查到这么多了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.30,0:21:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是我看中的人 果然优秀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.58,0:21:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.60,0:21:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在罗兰德发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.96,0:21:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有其真正意义
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.17,0:21:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会这么拼命 是为了莱纳·琉特吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.70,0:21:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了拯救世界而奋战不休的勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.73,0:21:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崩溃以后追求力量 最终被封印起来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.07,0:21:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而为了解除这封印
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.92,0:21:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吞噬了害怕寂寞的恶魔之力量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.63,0:21:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕寂寞的恶魔…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.62,0:21:45.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.95,0:21:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加斯塔克很快就将进攻中央大陆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.42,0:21:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该会和罗兰德正面冲突吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.34,0:21:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前 我要借你之手救出莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.18,0:22:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在席恩·阿斯塔尔背叛莱纳之前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.84,0:22:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.08,0:22:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席恩怎么会背叛莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.23,0:22:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堕落的黑暗勇者为了拯救世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.51,0:22:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将吞噬害怕寂寞的恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.05,0:22:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在比死更残酷的绝望 吞噬莱纳·琉特之前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.79,0:22:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要把他救出来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.64,0:22:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从堕落的黑暗勇者手中救出来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.29,0:22:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要带着莱纳回来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.26,0:22:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.63,0:22:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,单恋真痛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.70,0:22:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下 一切准备就绪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.21,0:22:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.10,0:22:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时机到来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.98,0:22:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要向未来前进
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.72,0:22:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让不再有泪水的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.34,0:22:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为现实
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.31,0:23:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加斯塔克万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.77,0:23:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前进
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.71,0:23:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳…

Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.26,0:23:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席恩…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.13,0:23:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,0)}{\fs40}最后一日
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.85,0:23:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢

